# Header Line Format

The header line gives information about the FIGfont. Here is an example showing the names of all parameters:

```pointer
flf2a$ 6 5 20 15 3 0 143 229
flf2a$: Signature
$: Hardblank
6: Height
5: Baseline
20: Max_Length
15: Old_Layout
3: Comment_Lines
0: Print_Direction
143: Full_Layout
229: Codetag_Count
```

The two layout parameters are closely related and fairly complex.
